oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The herd that I work with on the Integrated Resource Management (IRM) program is one that I had the privilege of working with very closely for several years before the IRM concept was developed. Because of this, the data I will be citing will be a combination of data from my pre-IRM work and the IRM team work.
